text: People with the COVID-19 vaccine are being tracked in real time via 5G cellular, and all that data can be hacked into to track you.

COVID-19 is fake and just a coverup of 5G technology
Google and Apple put a covid tracker on every phone.
The Covid-19 vaccines put people who have received them in danger if 5G is ‘cranked up’.
Covid-19 vaccines can cause people to become magnetized; are connected to 5G cell towers
